            . I AM a pawnbroker, and live in Shoreditch: the prosecutor is a neighbour of mine: the prisoner pledged these things with me; (producing a blue domask gown, a green silk gown, a sheet, a napkin, and three pewter plates.)</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. These two gowns, the napkin, and two plates, are my property.</p>
