                     <interp inst="t17650522-22-person274" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , for her use. I asked her what she had done with the money? she said, she had spent it all.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176505220023"></xptr>
            
